g is especially important because QMC is the only viable\ntechnique so far for calculating $\\kappa$ in multi-component systems at\nlow-temperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2015 17:20:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Oct 2015 14:58:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
