ar trend to the lighter systems, Au+Au and Cu+Cu, at\nsimilar energy 200 GeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2015 21:12:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-30"}
